50
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:04,580
Use this as a cushion.

51
00:04:28,990 --> 00:04:30,190
What's wrong?

52
00:04:30,910 --> 00:04:32,990
My tractor broke down!

53
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:00,290
Hello.

54
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:02,440
