55
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:05,970
-Have some tea.
-Okay.

56
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:08,030
Here, kid. Drink it.

57
00:05:08,370 --> 00:05:09,640
Thank you.

58
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:11,060
Have some tea.

59
00:05:12,990 --> 00:05:14,340
Thank you.

60
