Have some tea.

61
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,250
Have some tea.

62
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,340
Thank you.

63
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:20,540
Thank you.

64
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:21,870
Bye.

65
00:05:46,860 --> 00:05:49,600
Batay, your horses aren't following us.

66
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:52,580
Don't worry about the horses. Just watch the sheep.

67
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:53,840
Sheep are stupider.

68
00:05:55,020 --> 00:05:55,880
Dad.

69
00:05:56,670 --> 00:05:59,550
They're worried the horses will get lost.

70
00:06:00,710 --> 00:06:04,340
Horses are intelligent. They won't get lost.

71
