666
00:37:29,430 --> 00:37:31,070
She's young and immature.

667
00:37:31,390 --> 00:37:33,020
Don't be mad at her.

668
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:34,490
Please be magnanimous.

669
00:37:49,820 --> 00:37:51,390
Please be magnanimous.

