00:43:00,960 --> 00:43:02,170
Batay, my child.

750
00:43:02,200 --> 00:43:02,760
Auntie!

751
00:43:03,520 --> 00:43:04,410
Wenxiu.

752
00:43:05,190 --> 00:43:06,570
